|   |
|   |- Offset 3 -> D
|   |- Offset 4 -> E
|   |- Offset 5 -> F
|
--Segment-3
    |
    |- Offset 6 -> G
    |- Offset 7 -> H
    |- Offset 8 -> I

Ye Segments Kafka automatically create aur manage karta hai.

Application Developer ko normally Segments ke baare me directly deal nahi karna padta.


