7: CONSUMER GROUP
====================

Consumer Group Consumers ka ek logical group hota hai jo milkar kisi Kafka Topic ke Partitions ko aapas me divide karke messages consume karta hai.

----------
## NOTE :
----------
Har consumer group ka Kafka cluster me ek broker hota hai jo us group ka coordinator banta hai

---------------------
## IMPORTANT RULE :
---------------------

Ek Partition ko Ek consumer-group ke andar Sirf Ek Consumer Read Karega

## Example:
------------

Maan lo topic hai: Intro

and it has 1 partition. i.e Partition-0

Ab maan lo 5 consumers hai jo ki 'Intro' topic ko subscribe kiye hue hai 

Consumer-1 
Consumer-2 
Consumer-3 
Consumer-4 
Consumer-5

and ye pancho same consumer-group me hain. 

consumer-group = IntroProcessors

Ab Kafka in 5 consumers ko ek team samjhega.


Is consumer-group ka group-coordinator partition assignment kuch aisa kar sakta hai:

Partition-0 -> Consumer-1

Consumer-2 -> Idle
Consumer-3 -> Idle
Consumer-4 -> Idle
Consumer-5 -> Idle

Kyun?

Kyuki ek hi Partition available hai.

Aur ek Partition ko consumer-group ke andar ek hi Consumer consume kar sakta hai.

Baaki Consumers idle rahenge.


## IMPORTANT :
---------------

Agar do consumers alag consumer groups se hai to dono same Partition ko consume kar sakte hain.

Example:

Group-A
|
+--> Consumer-1

Group-B
|
+--> Consumer-2

To:

Partition-0

ko Consumer-1 bhi consume kar sakta hai

Aur

Consumer-2 bhi consume kar sakta hai

Kyuki dono alag Consumer Groups se belong karte hain.


