## Ab Sabse Important Question

Final output kya hoga? Kya mujhe "MY NAME IS ANURAG" milega?

Answer: NO. 

Kafka aisa guarantee nahi karta.

Kafka ko ye pata hi nahi hai ki:

MY
NAME
IS
ANURAG
