milkar ek sentence banate hain.

Kafka ke liye ye sirf 5 independent messages hain.


Consumer-1 sequentially read karega:
MY
ANURAG


Consumer-2 sequentially read karega:
NAME
Pandey


Consumer-3 sequentially read karega:
IS


Consumer-4 and Consumer-5 ideal rahenge.


Possible execution:   

Consumer-1 -> MY
Consumer-2 -> NAME
Consumer-1 -> ANURAG
Consumer-2 -> Pandey
Consumer-3 -> IS


To final result jo print ho sakta hai :

