NAME
IS
ANURAG
PANDEY

Lekin Kafka ye guarantee nahi karta.

Jab messages multiple Partitions me distribute ho jaate hain aur multiple Consumers parallel consume karte hain, tab Topic level ordering maintain nahi rehti.

Isse kehte hain: Global Ordering Problem

Kafka multiple Partitions ke across Global Ordering guarantee nahi karta.

Kafka sirf Partition ke andar ordering guarantee karta hai.


## Partition Ordering Kya Hai?

Partition-0

Offset 0: "MY"
Offset 1: "ANURAG"

