--------------------------------------
DELIVERY SEMANTICS EXACTLY KYA HAI?
--------------------------------------

Consumer ke paas 2 kaam hain:

1. Message Process Karna

2. Offset Commit Karna

In dono operations ke beech me crash aa sakta hai.

Delivery Semantics basically answer karti hai:

"Failure hone par ek message kitni baar process ho sakta hai?"

Delivery Semantics ek guarantee hai.

Kafka world me 3 guarantees hoti hain:

1. At Most Once

2. At Least Once

3. Exactly Once


1: AT MOST ONCE
-----------------

✔ Message will be delivered at most one time

✔ Duplicate delivery is not expected

✖ Message loss is possible


