------------------------------

Consumer pehle Offset Commit karta hai.

Uske baad Business Logic execute karta hai.

Flow:

Read Message
↓
Commit Offset
↓
Business Logic


## EXAMPLE :
---------------

Current State:

Offset 0 -> Order-101

Consumer read karta hai:

Read Order-101

Immediately:

